Dukkah (Egyptian Nut and Spice Mix)

1/4 c hazelnuts, toasted
3 tbsp sesame seeds, toasted
3 tbsp coriander seeds, toasted
2 tbsp pistachios, toasted
2 tbsp cashews, toasted
1 tbsp cumin seeds, toasted
1/2 tbsp fennel seeds, toasted
1 tsp kosher salt
1/2 tsp dried mint
1/4 tsp sugar
pinch red pepper flakes

Combine all ingredients in a food processor and pulse until a coarse spice mix forms. Use immediately or transfer to airtight container and store in the refrigerator for up to 2 weeks.
